  <p class="answer-first"><b>EPF is contributed at 12% each by employee and employer, ESI at 0.75% (employee) and 3.25% (employer) up to a Rs.21,000 wage ceiling, and professional tax is a state levy capped at Rs.2,500 per year.</b> Confirm state-specific PT slabs, which vary.</p>
